descriptionHtml:
Anise\'s Secret Spells

[b]
Description
[/b]
============

This mod add Anise Secret spells which she is hiding from whole world.
The spelltomes are at basement of Anise\'s cabin located near where the White River meets Lake Ilinalta.
The Following Spells are found in basement

1.CarbonCopy Self Spell
This spell can duplicate Your self Which fights for you in combat.You can create as many copies
of yourself as you like.

2.CarbonCopy Target Spell
This spell can duplicate any actor from game.The duplicated actor is your
friend and fights for you.The duplicated actor will be of same level
as the original actor

3.Money Spell
Ever wondered what to do with the dead bodies lying all over when the combat
end now this spell will turn dead bodies into gold.

4.HolyCow Spell
This Spell Can turns any actor into cow.

5.Chicken Spell
This Spell Can turn any actor into chicken.
